🚀 Built My First API-Based Project!

Excited to share my **Async Weather Tracker** 🌦️ — my first project where I implemented **API fetching using JavaScript**.

🔹 Fetches real-time weather data
🔹 Uses async/await for handling API calls
🔹 Displays temperature, humidity, wind speed, and conditions
🔹 Stores search history using localStorage
🔹 Clean and responsive UI

This project helped me deeply understand:

* API integration
* Promises, async/await
* DOM manipulation
* Real-world JavaScript workflow

🔗 Live Project: https://bajpaiabhinav2007.github.io/web-dev-assi.-2-Sem-2/

More improvements coming soon 🚀

